OL,3,CChannel swimmer goes viral as
OL,4,CAmericans believe she is crossing
OL,5,CAtlantic
OL,7,FTens of thousands of social media
OL,8,Fusers were left puzzled amid confusion
OL,9,Fover a post announcing plans to swim
OL,10,Ffrom Jersey to France in a single day.
OL,12,FGeorgia Mould, also known by her
OL,13,FTikTok handle @georgia swimming, made
OL,14,Fthe post on Easter Sunday, titled,
OL,15,F'Before I attempt to swim from Jersey
OL,16,Fto France, here's what you need to
OL,17,Fknow', with many American viewers
OL,18,Fmistakenly believing her challenge
OL,19,Fwould begin in New Jersey, USA.
OL,26,@uD@Wpo
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776757104
OL,3,CChannel swimmer goes viral as
OL,4,CAmericans believe she is crossing
OL,5,CAtlantic
OL,7,FMost of Georgia's recent posts have a
OL,8,Ffew hundred views, but this one went
OL,9,Fviral.
OL,11,FAs of Friday afternoon (17 April), it
OL,12,Fhas received more than 900,000 views
OL,13,Fand 2,500 comments - with many coming
OL,14,Ffrom the US State on the country's
OL,15,FEast Coast.
OL,17,FSocial media users expressed confusion
OL,18,Fover Georgia's attempt, with one
OL,19,Fsaying: "So you're telling me I could
OL,20,Fget a boat, drive to New Jersey and be
OL,21,Fin France in 8 hours, give or take???"
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776757104
OL,3,CChannel swimmer goes viral as
OL,4,CAmericans believe she is crossing
OL,5,CAtlantic
OL,7,FOthers admitted their mistaken belief
OL,8,Fthat Europe and America is closer than
OL,9,Fexpected: "I genuinely accepted you
OL,10,Fcan swim from NJ to France in 15
OL,11,Fmiles."
OL,13,FMeanwhile, for some, the post seemed
OL,14,Fto mark their discovery of Jersey
OL,15,Fitself: "Wait, I'd never considered
OL,16,Fthe concept of Old Jersey."
OL,18,FIn reality, New Jersey is estimated to
OL,19,Fbe approximately 3,700 miles from
OL,20,FFrance - significantly further than
OL,21,Fthe 14 Georgia will be swimming.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776757104
OL,3,CChannel swimmer goes viral as
OL,4,CAmericans believe she is crossing
OL,5,CAtlantic
OL,7,FShe will set off from Jersey, Channel
OL,8,FIslands, in August, and anticipates
OL,9,Fthe swim will take between seven and
OL,10,Ften hours to complete.
OL,12,FGeorgia has been left just as confused
OL,13,Fby the post's success as many of the
OL,14,Fsocial media users over her planned
OL,15,Fswim.
OL,17,FShe has since edited the caption to
OL,18,Ftry and set the record straight,
OL,19,Fsaying: "The original Jersey (island
OL,20,Fbetween England and France), not New
OL,21,FJersey".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
