OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776757104
OL,3,CChannel swimmer goes viral as
OL,4,CAmericans believe she is crossing
OL,5,CAtlantic
OL,7,FShe told ITV News: "It was just a
OL,8,Fquick post, and it somehow made it to
OL,9,FNew Jersey - I have no idea how - but
OL,10,Fas soon as it did the post just
OL,11,Fexploded and the comments kept coming.
OL,13,F"It was bringing my partner and I so
OL,14,Fmuch joy reading them every morning -
OL,15,Fit had never crossed my mind that the
OL,16,Ftwo places would be confused.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776757104
OL,3,CChannel swimmer goes viral as
OL,4,CAmericans believe she is crossing
OL,5,CAtlantic
OL,7,F"Some of the comments thought airlines
OL,8,Fhad been ripping them off with travel
OL,9,Ftimes, and others even compared me to
OL,10,Fthe Titanic. People had a blind belief
OL,11,Fthat I could swim across the Atlantic."
OL,13,FThis is not the first time Georgia has
OL,14,Fgone viral, or attempted a long swim.
OL,16,FIn July 2025, she successfully swam
OL,17,Facross the English Channel from
OL,18,FEngland to France in 11 hours and 51
OL,19,Fminutes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776757104
OL,3,CChannel swimmer goes viral as
OL,4,CAmericans believe she is crossing
OL,5,CAtlantic
OL,7,FShe raised around #10,000 for Cancer
OL,8,FResearch in the process - the same
OL,9,Fcharity she will be fundraising for in
OL,10,Fher swim this summer.
OL,12,FGeorgia documented her journey before
OL,13,Fand after the challenge, with some
OL,14,Fvideos garnering millions of views,
OL,15,Falthough the comments usually focused
OL,16,Fon her training - rather than the
OL,17,Ffeasibility of swimming across the
OL,18,FAtlantic.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
