OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776757104
OL,3,CChannel swimmer goes viral as
OL,4,CAmericans believe she is crossing
OL,5,CAtlantic
OL,7,FShe adds: "The whole reason I started
OL,8,Fmy TikTok was to reach 1,000
OL,9,Ffollowers, so that I could then put a
OL,10,Ffundraising link in my bio, which
OL,11,Fended up bringing in donations from
OL,12,Fcomplete strangers.
OL,14,F"I think the popularity I've got this
OL,15,Ftime around will help raise money for
OL,16,Fcharity once again.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
