OL,3,CChannel swimmer goes viral as
OL,4,CAmericans believe she is crossing
OL,5,CAtlantic
OL,7,F"I really appreciate all the support
OL,8,FI've got out of this. We all know the
OL,9,Finternet can be a harsh place
OL,10,Fsometimes, so it's been great to have
OL,11,Fsuch a nice experience on it."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
